headline: Cash-back credit cards: finding the best one for you
summary: Your credit card can pay you cash back, if you choose the right one for you. Companies like American Express (AXP), JP Morgan Chase (JPM), Costco (COST), Target (TGT), and Walmart (WMT) all offer cards with perks. But the key is choosing the right one for you. Yahoo Finance anchor Brad Smith breaks down the three basic types of cash-back cards and what to consider as you make your decisions. Click here for more on cash-back credit cards.
